PREREQUISITES:

   You'll need at least perl5.005_02 & Tk402.004

REALLY QUICK START GUIDE:

   perl tk_timesheet.pl <RETURN>


ABOUT TK TIMESHEET:

Are you a contractor, or a consultant who needs to work out their
weekly hours for invoicing purposes?

Are you less than keen to use Microsoft spreadsheet products
to do this?

Then "Tk Timesheet" is for you.

